node.title: Two arrests after incident in central Wellington
node.description: Police have arrested two people following an incident in Dixon Street, in Wellington's CBD this morning.
node.content:
["Police have arrested two people following an incident in Dixon Street, in Wellington's CBD this morning.", "", "
\nPhoto: RNZ / Cole Eastham-Farrelly\n
", "Police have not disclosed the nature of the incident but say two people have been taken to Wellington Hospital with injuries arising from the incident.", "Cordons are in place in the vicinity of Dixon Street while police conduct a scene examination."]
